==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wonderful
<hw>Won"der*ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Adapted to excite
wonder or admiration; surprising; strange; astonishing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Marvelous; amazing. See
<er>Marvelous</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Won"der*ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Won"der*ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wonderingly</ent>⟦br⟧
